Package it.unitn.disi.smatch.renderers.mapping

Interface Summary
IMappingRenderer An interface for mapping renderers.
 

Class Summary
DefaultHTMLMappingRenderer Renders a mapping into an HTML file.
PlainRenderer Writes only mapping part, that is cNod matrix.
PlainSortedRenderer Writes only mapping part, that is cNod matrix.
PlainXTopRenderer Writes only mapping part, that is cNod matrix, eXcluding Top node mappings.
TaxMEMappingRenderer Writes a mapping in a TaxME format.
